chatLinkSettings.info:
Configure chat links, which take effect in the chat of the token and in the chat of the Playground on the homepage.
In the link, {key} can replace the user's token, and {server} can replace the server address. For example: {'https://chat.oneapi.pro/#/?settings={"key":"sk-{key}","url":"{server}"}'}
If not configured, the following 4 links will be configured by default:
ChatGPT Next ： {'https://chat.oneapi.pro/#/?settings={"key":"{key}","url":"{server}"}'}
chatgpt-web-midjourney-proxy ： {'https://vercel.ddaiai.com/#/?settings={"key":"{key}","url":"{server}"}'}
AMA ： {'ama://set-api-key?server={server}&key={key}'}
opencat ： {'opencat://team/join?domain={server}&token={key}'}
Sorting rules: The larger the value, the higher the ranking, and the same value is sorted according to the configuration order

paymentSettings.alert:
Payment Settings:
1. USD Exchange Rate: Used to calculate the amount of recharge in USD
2. Minimum Recharge Amount (USD): Minimum recharge amount, in USD, enter an integer
3. All pages are calculated in USD, and the actual currency paid by the user is converted according to the currency set by the payment gateway
For example: A gateway sets the currency as CNY, the user pays 100 USD, then the actual payment amount is 100 * USD exchange rate
B gateway sets the currency as USD, the user pays 100 USD, then the actual payment amount is 100 USD

discount.label: Fixed Amount Recharge Discount
discount.placeholder: It is a JSON text, the key is the recharge amount, and the value is the discount

paymentSettings.discountInfo:
Fixed Amount Recharge Discount Example:
It is a JSON text, the key is the recharge amount, and the value is the discount. For example, {"10":0.9} means that a recharge of 10 USD is calculated at a 10% discount
Calculation formula: actual cost = (original value * discount + original value * discount * fee rate) * exchange rate

minAmount.label: Minimum Recharge Amount (USD)
minAmount.placeholder: e.g., 1, then the minimum recharge amount is 1 USD, please enter an integer

paymentSettings.title: Payment Settings

groupRatio.label: Group Ratio
groupRatio.placeholder: It is a JSON text, the key is the group name, and the value is the ratio

当涉及到知识库ID时，请前往开放平台的知识库模块进行创建或获取(是知识库ID不是: When it comes to the knowledge base ID, please go to the knowledge base module of the open platform to create or obtain it (it is the knowledge base ID, not the document ID!)

按照如下格式输入：APIKey-AppId，例如：fastgpt-0sp2gtv: Enter in the following format: APIKey-AppId, for example: fastgpt-0sp2gtvfdgyi4k30jwlgwf1i-64f335d84283f05518e9e041
按照如下格式输入：APIKey|SecretKey: Enter according to the following format: APIKey|SecretKey
按照如下格式输入：APISecret|groupID: Enter it in the following format: APISecret|groupID
按照如下格式输入：APPID|APISecret|APIKey: Enter it in the following format: APPID|APISecret|APIKey
按照如下格式输入：AppId|SecretId|SecretKey: Enter it in the following format: AppId|SecretId|SecretKey
按照如下格式输入：CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID|CLOUDFLAR: Enter it in the following format: CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID|CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN
按照如下格式输入：Region|AccessKeyID|SecretAccess: Enter it in the following format: Region|AccessKeyID|SecretAccessKey|SessionToken. SessionToken can be left blank.
按照如下格式输入：SecretId|SecretKey: Enter it in the following format: SecretId|SecretKey
本配置主要是用于使用cloudflare Zero Trust将端口暴露到公网时: This configuration is mainly used for the headers that need to be configured when using cloudflare Zero Trust to expose the port to the public network.
模型名称为coze-{bot_id}，你也可以直接使用 coze-* 通配符来匹: The model name is coze-{bot_id}. You can also directly use coze-* wildcards to match all models starting with coze.
模型名称映射， 你可以取一个容易记忆的名字来代替coze-{bot_id}，例如:
Model name mapping, you can replace coze-{bot_id} with an easy-to-remember name, for example: {"coze-translate": "coze-xxxxx"}. Note: If model mapping is used, the above model name must 
Use the name before mapping. In the above example, you should fill in coze-translate in the model (you can ignore it if coze-* is already used).
模型映射关系：例如用户请求A模型，实际转发给渠道的模型为B。: Model mapping relationship: for example, when user requests model A, the actual model forwarded to the channel is model B.
用于测试使用的模型，为空时无法测速,如：gpt-3.5-turbo，仅支持cha: The model used for testing cannot measure speed when empty. For example: gpt-3.5-turbo, only supports chat model.
请前往开放平台的知识库上传文档，然后使用知识库功能进行检索。: Please go to the knowledge base of the open platform to upload documents, and then use the knowledge base function to search.
请参考wiki中的文档获取key. https://github.com/Mar: Please refer to the documentation in the wiki to obtain the key. https://github.com/MartialBE/one-hub/wiki/VertexAI
请求模型时的知识库模板, 请查看文档填写，否则不用填写: Knowledge base template when requesting a model, please check the document to fill it in, otherwise there is no need to fill it in

请输入你部署的Ollama地址，例如：http://127.0.0.1:1143: Please enter the Ollama address you deployed, for example: http://127.0.0.1:11434. If you use cloudflare Zero Trust, you can fill in the authorization information in the plug-in below.
请输入插件参数，即 X-DashScope-Plugin 请求头的取值: Please enter the plug-in parameters, that is, the value of the X-DashScope-Plugin request header
请输入渠道对应的鉴权密钥: Please enter the authentication key corresponding to the channel
请输入版本号，例如：v1: Please enter the version number, for example: v1
请输入默认API版本，例如：2024-05-01-preview: Please enter the default API version, for example: 2024-05-01-preview
请选择该渠道所支持的模型,你也可以输入通配符*来匹配模型，例如：gpt-3.5*:
Please select the model supported by this channel. You can also enter the wildcard character * to match the model. For example: gpt-3.5*, which means that all models starting with gpt-3.5 are supported. The * sign can only be used in the last digit, and there must be characters in front of it. 
, for example: gpt-3.5* is correct, *gpt-3.5 is wrong
请选择该渠道所支持的用户组: Please select the user group supported by this channel
请随意填写: Please feel free to fill in
输入后，会替换请求地址中的v1，例如：freeapi，则请求chat时会变成ht: After input, v1 in the request address will be replaced. For example: freeapi, when requesting chat, it will become https://xxx.com/freeapi/chat/completions. If you need to disable the version number, please enter disable
